item.title: Are the Kardashians Witches? Breaking Down the Kardashian Kurse
item.description: Are the Kardashians witches who curse the men they're with? Today I dive into this internet theory with floozie expert Kora to find out what's really going on. We peer into the history of witchcraft, the layers of misogyny surrounding this practice, and end the episode with some recent Kardashian blind items. Feed: https://feeds.simplecast.com/d591w4bu
